name: BURN ME ASAP
description: Well done! You made it to round 3! Now, I will explain how to get to round 4! Burn this NFT by 00:01 UTC, 19th of February 2022. You will receive HXRE WE GX AGAIN when I see the burn. If you don't burn by then then you wont get into round 4 by default. HOWEVER, upon getting the HXRE WE GX AGAIN you can trade, sell, burn whatever, that wont disqualify you per se. But on the 26th of February at 00:01UTC whoever holds one will proceed to round 4, getting you or anyone back in the running.
